This,REST,API,is,an,Ajax,Load,More,add,on,for,Wordpress,that,allows,infinite,scrolling,The,WordPress,REST,API,V,add,on,works,by,routing,the,standard,Ajax,Load,More,requests,through,to,API,endpoints,for,data,retrieval,The,data,is,returned,as,JSON,displayed,using,JS,templates,on,the,front,end,of,your,website,Using,a,simple,GET,request,a,JavaScript,Repeater,Template,and,a,custom,endpoint,developed,specifically,for,Ajax,Load,More,users,are,able,to,access,website,data,and,infinite,scroll,the,results,using,the,WP,REST,API